        },
        {
          "title": "FUNDING",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "NCDIT is supported financially by several primary funding sources, including cost recovery from state agencies and local governments for IT staffing and services, 911 fees from telecom vendors and direct general fund appropriations.",
